      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Wen-Jie Tseng</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:150px;\"><a href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=800&amp;wppa-album=3&amp;wppa-cover=0&amp;wppa-occur=1&amp;wppa-photo=45\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/f/f1/WenJieTseng.jpg\" width=\"148\" height=\"216\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:WenJieTseng.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Wen-Jie Tseng <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Wen-Jie Tseng</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientist affiliated with the Department of Computer Science, <a href=\"/National_Chiao_Tung_University\" title=\"National Chiao Tung University\">National Chiao Tung University</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hsinchu\">Hsinchu</a>. He is co-author of the <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chimo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chimo (page does not exist)\">Chimo</a>, and further co-author of two programs which won their respective tournaments at the <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a> in Yokohama 2013 , the <a href=\"/Chinese_Dark_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Dark Chess\">Chinese Dark Chess</a> engine <i>DarkKnight</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> , and the <a href=\"/Connect6\" title=\"Connect6\">Connect6</a> engine <i>Mobile6</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2013</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2014\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=849&amp;wppa-album=6&amp;wppa-cover=0&amp;wppa-occur=1&amp;wppa-photo=83\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"DarkChess2013.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/ab/DarkChess2013.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"424\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">Yokohama 2013</a> award ceremony <a href=\"/Chinese_Dark_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Dark Chess\">Chinese Dark Chess</a>, <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a> (Operator Yahari, Bronze),<br />\n<a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (DarkKnight, Gold), <a href=\"/Cheng-Wei_Chou\" title=\"Cheng-Wei Chou\">Cheng-Wei Chou</a> (Diablo, Silver), and <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2013\">2013</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2013\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Ching-Hua_Kuo\" title=\"Ching-Hua Kuo\">Ching-Hua Kuo</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bo-Han_Lin&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bo-Han Lin (page does not exist)\">Bo-Han Lin</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://kaigi.org/jsai/webprogram/2013/paper-138.html\">A Supervised Learning Method for Chinese Chess Programs</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://2013.conf.ai-gakkai.or.jp/english-info\">JSAI2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://kaigi.org/jsai/webprogram/2013/pdf/138.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lung-Ping_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lung-Ping Chen (page does not exist)\">Lung-Ping Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>TCGA 2013 Computer Game Tournaments</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ting-Han_Wei\" title=\"Ting-Han Wei\">Ting-Han Wei</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>MOBILE 6 Wins Connect6 Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (<b>2013</b>).  <i>DARKNIGHT Wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ting-Han_Wei\" title=\"Ting-Han Wei\">Ting-Han Wei</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>MOBILE 6 Wins Connect6 Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#Connect6\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Pohsuan_She&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Pohsuan She (page does not exist)\">Pohsuan She</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>HAPPYNOGO Wins NOGO Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#NoGo\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014\">2014</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2014\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lung-Pin_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lung-Pin Chen (page does not exist)\">Lung-Pin Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Der-Johng_Sun\" title=\"Der-Johng Sun\">Der-Johng Sun</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Nonogram Tournament in Olympiad Yokohama 2013</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#37_1\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol 37, No. 1</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#Nonogram\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ting-Han_Wei\" title=\"Ting-Han Wei\">Ting-Han Wei</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Chao-Chin_Liang\" title=\"Chao-Chin Liang\">Chao-Chin Liang</a>, <a href=\"/Bing-Tsung_Chiang\" title=\"Bing-Tsung Chiang\">Bing-Tsung Chiang</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Chang-Shing_Lee\" title=\"Chang-Shing Lee\">Chang-Shing Lee</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Job-Level Algorithms for Connect6 Opening Position Analysis</i>. <a href=\"/index.php?title=ECAI_CGW_2014&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ECAI CGW 2014 (page does not exist)\">ECAI CGW 2014</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chu-Hsuan_Hsueh\" title=\"Chu-Hsuan Hsueh\">Chu-Hsuan Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>Strength Improvement and Analysis for an MCTS-Based Chinese Dark Chess Program</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_14\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 14\">Advances in Computer Games 14</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ting-Han_Wei\" title=\"Ting-Han Wei\">Ting-Han Wei</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Chao-Chin_Liang\" title=\"Chao-Chin Liang\">Chao-Chin Liang</a>, <a href=\"/Bing-Tsung_Chiang\" title=\"Bing-Tsung Chiang\">Bing-Tsung Chiang</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Chang-Shing_Lee\" title=\"Chang-Shing Lee\">Chang-Shing Lee</a> (<b>2015</b>).  <i>Job-Level Algorithms for Connect6 Opening Book Construction</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#38_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 38, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bo-Han_Lin&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bo-Han Lin (page does not exist)\">Bo-Han Lin</a>, <a href=\"/Chia-Hui_Chang\" title=\"Chia-Hui Chang\">Chia-Hui Chang</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/6785996/\">Job-Level Alpha-Beta Search</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 7, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>DarkKnight Wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#39_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 39, No. 2</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/19th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"19th Computer Olympiad\">19th Computer Olympiad 2016</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Chimo wins Chinese chess tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 2</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/20th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"20th Computer Olympiad\">20th Computer Olympiad 2017</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tinghan_Wei&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tinghan Wei (page does not exist)\">Tinghan Wei</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Comparison Training for Computer Chinese Chess</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1801.07411\">arXiv:1801.07411</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=521\">Wen-Jie Tseng's ICGA Tournaments</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wen-Jie_Tseng&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">Yokohama 2013</a>, Silver medal for <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=178\">Chimo</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=800\">Photos 2013 Events: day 3</a>, <a href=\"/ICGA\" title=\"ICGA\">ICGA</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>DARKNIGHT Wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Ting-Han_Wei\" title=\"Ting-Han Wei\">Ting-Han Wei</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Sh